reviewText: A minor classic.  Very much worth viewing - particularly the young Henry Fonda.
A Central New York Classic!! Canastota, Manlius, Syracuse and Cooperstown...the whole 9 yards!

This is a movie I had remembered as a young girl......It had been one of my favorites...  I was excited when I seen it had been released at Amazon........  This had even been where I had first heard the name CHAD and decided that if ever when I grew up and had a son his name would be CHAD.......I loved this movie then and STILL Love it now..............It is just a Good movie for anyone to watch............... It makes your Heart  Smile !!!!!!!!!!!
I am very happy with pack
